<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#090a0f">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">

    <title>站点升级中 - 🌍𝐌𝐉全球华人之家🕊️</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/ico" href="https://1818461212.v.123pan.cn/1818461212/%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/mj.lyimc.top/logo.jpg">

    <style>
        :root {
            --mj-gold: #f3cf7a;
            --mj-dark: #090a0f;
            --gold-glow: rgba(243, 207, 122, 0.3);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        /* 强制打上实体深色底纹，防止系统橡皮筋回弹露白 */
        html, body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--mj-dark) !important;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* 梦幻流动夜空背景 */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #14162b 0%, var(--mj-dark) 100%);
            z-index: -2;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* 星尘微粒背景 */
        .starfield {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='300' height='300' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Ccircle cx='40' cy='50' r='1.2' fill='%23f3cf7a' opacity='0.6'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='150' cy='180' r='1' fill='%23ffffff' opacity='0.4'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='230' cy='90' r='1.5' fill='%23f3cf7a' opacity='0.7'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='80' cy='240' r='1' fill='%23ffffff' opacity='0.5'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* 核心内容剧场卡片 */
        .maintenance-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        /* 专属艺术 Logo 头像缩放氛围 */
        .logo-box {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .mj-logo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(243, 207, 122, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--gold-glow);
            animation: logoPulse 4s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes logoPulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--gold-glow); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 45px rgba(243, 207, 122, 0.6); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            color: var(--mj-gold);
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(243, 207, 122, 0.3);
        }

        .notice-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* =========================================
           奢华流金动态进度条组件
           ========================================= */
        .progress-wrapper {
            width: 280px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .progress-track {
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 2px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 65%; /* 👈 你可以在这里手动调整当前更新的百分比 */
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f3cf7a, #ffffff, #f3cf7a);
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--mj-gold), 0 0 6px #ffffff;
            animation: flowLight 2s linear infinite;
        }
        .progress-status {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            margin-top: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .progress-num {
            color: var(--mj-gold);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @keyframes flowLight {
            0% { background-position: 100% 0%; }
            100% { background-position: -100% 0%; }
        }

        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 手机端极端屏幕专项防叠放适配 */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: 3px; }
            .notice-text { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 25px; }
            .mj-logo { width: 100px; height: 100px; }
            .progress-wrapper { width: 220px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="starfield"></div>

    <div class="maintenance-container">
        <div class="logo-box">
        </div>
        
        <h1>MJBEAUTY 升级维护中</h1>
        
        <p class="notice-text">
            为了带给你更极致的视听特展体验<br>
            华人之家空间站正在进行内核重构，请稍事等待
        </p>

        <div class="progress-wrapper">
            <div class="progress-track">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-status">
                <span>Neverland 补给中...</span>
                <span class="progress-num">65%</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        LOVE LIVES FOREVER | MJBEAUTY.TOP<br>
        思念永无止境，星光破茧成蝶
    </footer>

</body>
</html>